General.Name: Inversiones Doalca SOCIMI SA
General.Description: Inversiones Doalca Socimi, S.A., a real estate investment company, leases and rents real estate properties in Spain. Its real estate properties include offices and commercial premises. As of December 31, 2015, the company owned a portfolio of 11 properties with a constructed area of approximately 42,000 square meters and a total leasable area of approximately 32,000 square meters. Inversiones Doalca Socimi, S.A. was incorporated in 1998 and is headquartered in Madrid, Spain.
